# Android 6.0 SettingsUI的结构

Settings应用的影响波及了Android系统大部分的功能模块，如何快速将UI设置项和代码关联起来是本文将说明的内容。

本文通过分析Android 6.0原生代码，解释Settings应用的UI构成。

## Settings入口
Android的应用入口在`AndroidManifest.xml`中定义，由Settings的`AndroidManifest.xml`文件可知其入口为：
[AndroidManifest.xml#119](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/AndroidManifest.xml#111)

```xml
<!-- Alias for launcher activity only, as this belongs to each profile. -->
<activity-alias android:name="Settings"
        android:targetActivity="Settings">
    <intent-filter>
        <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
    </intent-filter>
</activity-alias>
```
打开Settings类，该类继承自SettingsActivity，在类中又整齐的定义了各种SettingsActivity的子类：
[Settings.java#24](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/Settings.java#24)

```java
/**
 * Top-level Settings activity
 */
public class Settings extends SettingsActivity {
    /*
    * Settings subclasses for launching independently.
    */
    public static class BluetoothSettingsActivity extends SettingsActivity { /* empty */ }
    public static class WirelessSettingsActivity extends SettingsActivity { /* empty */ }
    ...
}
```

于是SettingsActivity便是真正的Settings应用的入口。

## `Settings>More...`的流程
为便于理解，用一个测试用例来说明Settings UI的生成过程，如：

1. 进入SettingsActivity
2. 点击`More...`菜单

其流程图如下：

<pre>

</pre>

下面逐个说明各步骤的具体操作。

### 1. 进入SettingsActivity
进入settings的过程也就是应用初始化的过程。结合上面的流程图，从UI初始化的角度出发，该过程包含三个阶段：

#### step1~step7
这个过程中主要完成两件工作：
1. 根据当前的activity是否为主界面设置区分变量`SettingsActivity.mIsShowingDashboard`
2. 根据`mIsShowingDashboard`的值载入对应的`PreferenceFragment`

首先来看看设置`mIsShowingDashboard`的判断条件 -- 当处理intent的组件名称为`Settings.class`时，当前即为主界面：
[SettingsActivity.java#539](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/SettingsActivity.java#559)

```java
@Override
protected void onCreate(Bundle savedState) {
    final ComponentName cn = intent.getComponent();
    final String className = cn.getClassName();

    mIsShowingDashboard = className.equals(Settings.class.getName());
}
```

确认了当前是否为主界面后，进行载入相应的布局文件：
[SettingsActivity.java#580](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/SettingsActivity.java#580)

```java
@Override
protected void onCreate(Bundle savedState) {
    setContentView(mIsShowingDashboard ?
            R.layout.settings_main_dashboard : R.layout.settings_main_prefs);
}
```

最后根据`mIsShowingDashboard`加载对应的`FragmentName`：
[SettingsActivity.java#617](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/SettingsActivity.java#617)

```java
@Override
protected void onCreate(Bundle savedState) {
    if (!mIsShowingDashboard) {
        ...
    } else {
        switchToFragment(DashboardSummary.class.getName(), null, false, false,
                mInitialTitleResId, mInitialTitle, false);
    }
}
```

#### step10~step14
这个阶段会生成菜单的数据结构，通过加载[dashboard_categories.xml](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/res/xml/dashboard_categories.xml)文件，
创建出`SettingsActivity.mCategories`对象。
[SettingsActivity.java#1061](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/SettingsActivity.java#1061)

```java

```

下表为XML中tag和创建对象的对应关系

|class obj|<tag>|
|---------|-----|
|DashboardCategory|`<dashboard-category>`|
|DashboardTile|`<dashboard-tile>`|

下表为XML中tag属性和创建对象属性的对应关系

|class.field|xml attr|
|-----------|--------|
|DashboardCategory.id|android:id|
|DashboardCategory.titleRes|android:title|
|DashboardCategory.key|android:key|
|||
|DashboardTile.id|android:id|
|DashboardTile.resourceId|android:title|
|DashboardTile.iconRes|android:icon|
|DashboardTile.fragment|android:fragment|

生成`SettingsActivity.mCategories`对象后，会根据当前系统情况做一次菜单项过滤：
[SettingsActivity.java#1221](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/SettingsActivity.java#1221)

```java
private void updateTilesList(List<DashboardCategory> target) {
    ...
    for (int i = 0; i < size; i++) {

            id = (int) tile.id;

                }

            ...
        ...
    }
}
```


#### step15~step17
这个阶段比较简单，就是根据上一个阶段生成的`ArrayList<DashboardCategory>`对象`mCategories`生成对应的视图。
然后添加到`ViewGroup`对象`mDashboard`中，整个UI构建过程完毕
[DashboardSummary.java#127](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/dashboard/DashboardSummary.java#127)

````java
private void rebuildUI(Context context) {
    for (...) {
        DashboardCategory category = categories.get(n);
        View categoryView = mLayoutInflater.inflate(R.layout.dashboard_category, mDashboard, false);
        ViewGroup categoryContent =
                (ViewGroup) categoryView.findViewById(R.id.category_content);

        for (...) {
            DashboardTile tile = category.getTile(i);
            DashboardTileView tileView = new DashboardTileView(context);
            categoryContent.addView(tileView);
        }

        // Add the category
        mDashboard.addView(categoryView);
    }
}
````

### 2. 点击`More...`菜单

当Settings界面创建完成后，`DashboardTileView`负责监听按键事件。
用户按下各菜单时，通过`DashboardTileView`中绑定对象`mTile`获取要加载的fragment的名称，
并将其存入`intent`的`SettingsActivity.EXTRA_SHOW_FRAGMENT`字段中：
[Utils.java#715](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/Utils.java#715)

    public static Intent onBuildStartFragmentIntent(Context context, String fragmentName,
            Bundle args, String titleResPackageName, int titleResId, CharSequence title,
            boolean isShortcut) {
        intent.putExtra(SettingsActivity.EXTRA_SHOW_FRAGMENT, fragmentName);
        return intent;
    }


此时intent的内容如下：

    Intent { act=android.intent.action.MAIN cmp=com.android.settings/.SubSettings (has extras) }
    ComponentInfo{com.android.settings/com.android.settings.SubSettings}
    Bundle[{:settings:show_fragment_title=More, :settings:show_fragment_title_res_package_name=null, :settings:show_fragment=com.android.settings.WirelessSettings, :settings:show_fragment_as_shortcut=false, :settings:show_fragment_title_resid=2131493177, :settings:show_fragment_args=null}]

最后在`SubSettings` Activity中加载该`fragment`
[SettingsActivity.java#553](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/SettingsActivity.java#553)

    protected void onCreate(Bundle savedState) {
        // Getting Intent properties can only be done after the super.onCreate(...)
        final String initialFragmentName = intent.getStringExtra(EXTRA_SHOW_FRAGMENT);
        ...
        if (!mIsShowingDashboard) {
            ...
            switchToFragment(initialFragmentName, initialArguments, true, false,
                    mInitialTitleResId, mInitialTitle, false);
        } else {
            ...
        }
    }

## 通过Debug快速找到载入的fragment
由于载入fragment过程中没有打印相应的log，所以通过debug的方式是快速获取待加载`fragment`名称的有效方法。

通过上面的分析，将断点打在`Utils.onBuildStartFragmentIntent`方法上，
查看存入`SettingsActivity.EXTRA_SHOW_FRAGMENT`的值便可以知道待载入`fragment`的名称。
[Utils.java#715](http://androidxref.com/6.0.1_r10/xref/packages/apps/Settings/src/com/android/settings/Utils.java#715)

<pre>
<img src="data:image/png;base64," />
</pre>

上图中`EXTRA_SHOW_FRAGMENT`对应的值为`com.android.settings.WirelessSettings`，直接在代码中搜索`WirelessSettings`文件就可以查看代码了。
